@startuml
title State diagram for the Ott Based System Mini Reel class

[*] --> Idle

state "Idle" as Idle
Idle : entry/To action
Idle : do/Remain in same state
Idle : exit/Create Account / Watch Video
Idle : exit/Invalid registration

state "Create Account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/Create Account
CreateAccount : do/Create account after validating
CreateAccount : exit/Watch Video / Invalid registration

state "Invalid registration" as InvalidRegistration
InvalidRegistration : entry/Invalid registration
InvalidRegistration : do/Cannot register
InvalidRegistration : exit/Abnormal termination

state "Watch Video" as WatchVideo
WatchVideo : entry/Watch Video
WatchVideo : do/Watch video after login
WatchVideo : exit/Upload Video / Save Video

state "Upload Video" as UploadVideo
UploadVideo : entry/Upload Video
UploadVideo : do/Upload video
UploadVideo : exit/Save Video / Discussion

state "Save Video" as SaveVideo
SaveVideo : entry/Save Video
SaveVideo : do/Save video in likes list
SaveVideo : exit/View Saved Videos / Discussion

state "View Saved Videos" as ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos : entry/View Saved Videos
ViewSavedVideos : do/View saved videos
ViewSavedVideos : exit/Discussion

state "Discussion" as Discussion
Discussion : entry/Discussion
Discussion : do/Enter discussion option
Discussion : exit/End

state "End" as End
End : entry/End
End : do/End
End : exit/[*]

Idle --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> WatchVideo
WatchVideo --> UploadVideo
UploadVideo --> SaveVideo
SaveVideo --> ViewSavedVideos
ViewSavedVideos --> Discussion
Discussion --> End

InvalidRegistration --> [*]
@enduml
